##### Notes
Industrial Complex - Hostage Rescue

Counter-Terrorists: Enter the main warehouse
and rescue the hostages. 
Take out the Terrorists without 
jeopardizing the hostages.

Terrorists: Prevent Counter-Terrorist
force from rescuing the hostages. 

Other Notes: There are 4 hostages in 
this mission. The map is based on my previous map, dm\_industrial\_final.
